## Key Features

List the key features of your project.



1. Robust Multi-format File Ingest: Automatic text extraction from PDF, DOCX, PPTX, TXT, MD, and CSV.
2. SQLite Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF) Hybrid Search:  Blends vector semantic matches with BM25 Okapi keywords for precision.
3. Similarity Refusal Guard Automatic rejection of low-confidence questions :(similarity score < 0.6) with a polite notification.
4. Access Control Scoping : Personal (owner-only), Team (channel-only), and Org-wide (all users) access boundaries.
5. Contextual Multi-turn QA: Automatically builds conversational queries using recent context for re-retrieval.
6. LLM Fallback Search: Falls back to returning raw document text segments if the local LLM is temporarily offline.

